faqs.question: How much do lessons cost?
faqs.answer: Our standard rate is $60 per hour. We also offer a package of 10 lessons for $550, which saves you $50!

faqs.question: Do you provide the car for the test?
faqs.answer: Yes, beta! For a small fee of $100, you can use our safe and insured training car for your DMV driving test. We will even pick you up and warm you up before the test.

faqs.question: what is the refund policy?
faqs.answer: We understand life happens. Cancellations made 24 hours in advance get a full refund. Less than that, we have to charge a small fee to pay our instructors.
